Name: TradeTime
Description: TradeTime - Time (GMT) when the trade was filled

Name: TradeID
Description: Unique identifier for a trading event. Event can fill, order submission, reject or other event related to trading workflow

Name: Side
Description: Trade side. "B” for buy and "S” for sell.

Name: LP
Description: Executing LP - counterparty to the trade.

Name: Account
Description: Name of the underlying client this ParentOrderID executed on behalf of

Name: Trader
Description: The name of a trader associated with this TradeID

Name: TradeCcy
Description:
Denomination Currency for TradeQuantity and OrderQuantity. For example
    EUR.

Name: ProductType
Description: Type of product traded. For example SPOT

Name: NumLPs
Description: Total number of LPs in the stack

Name: SecondBestPrice
Description: The second best price in the stack

Name: BestBid
Description: The best Bid price in the stack

Name: BestAsk
Description: The best Ask price in the stack
